### **1. Email from a student to their professor**

**Subject:** Request for Extension on Assignment Submission

Respected Sir/Ma’am,

I hope you are doing well.

I am writing to kindly request an extension for the submission of my assignment due on 30-03-2026. Due to unforeseen circumstances, I was unable to complete the assignment on time.

I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused and assure you that I am working on completing it as soon as possible. I kindly request you to grant me an extension of a few days.

I would be grateful for your consideration.

Thank you for your time and understanding.

Yours sincerely,
**Nayan Chandravanshi**
**25MIM10125**

